'''柯克·道格拉斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Kirk Douglas'''}}，原名'''Issur Danielovitch Demsky'''，{{bd|1916年|12月9日|2020年|2月5日|catIdx=Douglas}}），美國[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]電影演員，猶太人<ref>{{cite web|first=Hadley|last=Freeman|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/feb/12/kirk-douglas-i-never-thought-id-live-to-100-thats-shocked-me|title=Kirk Douglas: ‘I never thought I’d live to 100. That’s shocked me’|work=The Guardian|date=February 12, 2017|accessdate=May 10, 2018|archive-date=2020-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418211444/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/feb/12/kirk-douglas-i-never-thought-id-live-to-100-thats-shocked-me|dead-url=no}}</ref>。寇克曾1950年代三次入圍[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳男主角皆未得獎，1996年獲頒[[奧斯卡終身成就獎|奧斯卡終身成就獎]]，2001年也獲得第51屆[[柏林影展|柏林影展]]終身成就獎，獲獎原因是「表現出義勇先鋒形象及美國式[[英雄主義|英雄主義]]」；實至名歸。1999年，他被美國電影學會選為[[百年百大明星|百年來最偉大的男演員]]第17名。

== 早年境況 ==
寇克·道格拉斯出生於美國紐約<ref>{{cite news | title = Kirk Douglas - Biography | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000018/bio | work = IMDb | accessdate = 2017-11-24 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108190708/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000018/bio | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他的父母是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|first=John|last=Plessel|url=https://www.dailynews.com/2016/12/08/5-reasons-to-celebrate-actor-kirk-douglas-on-his-100th-birthday/|title=5 reasons to celebrate actor Kirk Douglas on his 100th birthday|work=Los Angeles Daily News|date=December 8, 2016|accessdate=May 10, 2018|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331170509/https://www.dailynews.com/2016/12/08/5-reasons-to-celebrate-actor-kirk-douglas-on-his-100th-birthday/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Brad|last=Darrach|url=http://people.com/archive/kirk-douglas-vol-30-no-14/|title=Kirk Douglas|work=People magazine|date=October 3, 1988|accessdate=May 10, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511013051/http://people.com/archive/kirk-douglas-vol-30-no-14/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-37934804|title=Kirk Douglas honoured by World Jewish Congress|work=BBC|date=November 10, 2016|accessdate=May 10, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127063710/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-37934804|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thejc.com/lifestyle/interviews/hollywood-gladiator-kirk-douglas-has-his-eyes-set-on-a-third-barmitzvah-1.36378|title=Hollywood gladiator Kirk Douglas has his eyes set on a third barmitzvah|accessdate=May 25, 2018|date=September 20, 2012|last=Paskin|first=Barbra|work=The Jewish Chronicle|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331170526/https://www.thejc.com/lifestyle/interviews/hollywood-gladiator-kirk-douglas-has-his-eyes-set-on-a-third-barmitzvah-1.36378|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的表演天賦在紐約的美國戲劇藝術學院被注意到。

== 個人生活 ==
=== 家庭 ===
寇克·道格拉斯曾結過兩次婚：第一任妻子是Diana Douglas（原名是Diana Love Dill），兩人於1943年結婚，1951年離異，育有二名兒子，包括亦是著名演員的[[麥克·道格拉斯|麥克·道格拉斯]]；第二任妻子是Anne Buydens，兩人於1954年結婚，育有二子<ref>{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Tugend|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/books/219534/new-book-reveals-lifetime-love-letters-kirk-douglas-wife/|title=New book reveals a lifetime of love letters between Kirk Douglas and wife|work=Jewish Journal|date=May 25, 2017|accessdate=May 10, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511013417/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/books/219534/new-book-reveals-lifetime-love-letters-kirk-douglas-wife/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 逝世 ===
道格拉斯於2020年2月5日在加州[[比佛利山|比佛利山]]的家中去世，享嵩壽103歲。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-kirk-douglas-snap-story.html |title = Kirk Douglas dead at 103; ‘Spartacus’ star helped end Hollywood blacklist |author = Dennis Mclellan |date = 2020-02-05 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |access-date = 2020-02-06 |archive-date = 2021-02-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210220164029/https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-kirk-douglas-snap-story.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

